Phuak: OK.

00:54:10.800 --> 00:54:14.200
Billkin: Here, try it and see
if it's "grab, grab" or crunchy.

00:54:15.400 --> 00:54:18.450
Phuak: Crunchy!

00:54:18.450 --> 00:54:19.180
Billkin: Crunchy?

00:54:19.180 --> 00:54:19.190
[Crunchy!]

00:54:19.190 --> 00:54:19.750
Phuak: Crunchy!

00:54:19.750 --> 00:54:21.140
Billkin: One more bite. One more.

00:54:21.140 --> 00:54:21.850
Billkin: One more bite.

00:54:21.850 --> 00:54:23.110
Phuak: I know already!

00:54:23.580 --> 00:54:25.850
Phuak: Crunchy!

00:54:25.900 --> 00:54:27.430
Billkin: Your answer is...

00:54:28.920 --> 00:54:28.990
Billkin: Correct!

00:54:28.990 --> 00:54:31.250
[What is the first bite
of Choco Crush Lava like?]

00:54:31.250 --> 00:54:32.710
Billkin: Wow, so crunchy.

00:54:41.050 --> 00:54:42.450
Daou: Oat landed on his feet.

00:54:42.450 --> 00:54:44.050
NuNew: Oat's dive was so graceful.

00:54:44.050 --> 00:54:44.920
Daou: Oat, your dive was so graceful.

00:54:44.920 --> 00:54:45.480
Oat: What?

00:54:45.480 --> 00:54:46.360
NuNew: Your dive was so graceful.

00:54:46.360 --> 00:54:48.460
Oat: I only hear the crunching sound.

00:54:50.690 --> 00:54:52.220
Billkin: Next question.

00:54:52.920 --> 00:54:55.010
Billkin: Here's the next question.

00:54:55.890 --> 00:54:58.490
Billkin: In this picture
I'm about to show you,

00:54:59.080 --> 00:55:01.410
Billkin: how many faces have been merged?

00:55:01.790 --> 00:55:03.920
[Guess how many faces have been merged
in this picture]

00:55:04.420 --> 00:55:06.850
Phuak: Me, me, me!

00:55:06.850 --> 00:55:09.120
Daou: Me! Me!

00:55:09.120 --> 00:55:10.700
Ink: Daou, I'm at my limit.

00:55:10.700 --> 00:55:10.720
[Phuak]

00:55:10.720 --> 00:55:11.830
Billkin: Phuak!

00:55:14.190 --> 00:55:14.980
Oat: Me!

00:55:16.050 --> 00:55:17.650
Oat: Anyone, please hear me!

00:55:20.050 --> 00:55:20.910
Phuak: 5 faces.

00:55:21.220 --> 00:55:22.220
Billkin: 5 faces!

00:55:22.720 --> 00:55:23.870
[Guess how many faces have been merged
in this picture]

00:55:23.870 --> 00:55:24.800
Billkin: Wrong!

00:55:27.020 --> 00:55:27.950
Billkin: Wrong!

00:55:35.870 --> 00:55:37.850
[Beep!]

00:55:40.020 --> 00:55:44.020
Oat: Jerk! I'm turning pale from
whistling, and you still won't pick me?

00:55:44.650 --> 00:55:46.190
Oat: Request for VTR!
[T/N: Playback the recording]

00:55:46.190 --> 00:55:47.650
Billkin: OK, VTR. Play it!

00:55:53.790 --> 00:55:54.850
Billkin: Tay! Tay!

00:55:55.480 --> 00:55:56.020
Tay: 4!

00:55:56.890 --> 00:55:58.090
Ink: Tay, don't. Tay.

00:55:58.690 --> 00:55:59.690
Billkin: 4 faces.

00:55:59.980 --> 00:56:01.650
Billkin: Your answer is...

00:56:01.860 --> 00:56:02.020
[Guess how many faces have been merged
in this picture]

00:56:02.020 --> 00:56:03.080
Billkin: Correct!

00:56:04.120 --> 00:56:05.980
Tay: Face, eyes, nose, and mouth.

00:56:06.850 --> 00:56:08.850
Billkin: There are…

00:56:08.850 --> 00:56:09.580
Billkin: One

00:56:09.850 --> 00:56:10.980
Billkin: is Daou.

00:56:11.620 --> 00:56:12.620
Billkin: And Oat,

00:56:12.790 --> 00:56:14.640
Billkin: Phuak, and Ink.

00:56:16.470 --> 00:56:16.480
[Exhausted]

00:56:16.480 --> 00:56:17.940
Ink: Gosh, I'm at my limit.

00:56:21.690 --> 00:56:23.690
Tay: Come on! I'll take Ink's place!

00:56:24.120 --> 00:56:25.890
Ink: Wow, really?

00:56:26.190 --> 00:56:27.320
Ink: Do you mean it?

00:56:27.320 --> 00:56:28.190
Tay: Yes.

00:56:32.690 --> 00:56:35.550
Ink: Oh, I'm gonna cry.
He took my punishment for me!

00:56:35.790 --> 00:56:37.450
Daou: Aw. See? He is so caring.

00:56:40.500 --> 00:56:43.550
[Her kind big brother]

00:56:44.080 --> 00:56:45.250
Tay: I just want the points.

00:56:45.250 --> 00:56:46.320
Ink: Oh.

00:56:46.720 --> 00:56:50.290
Ink: Oh, you. You want points, but you
still helped me take the punishment.

00:56:50.290 --> 00:56:51.440
Daou: Aw, so cute.

00:56:52.420 --> 00:56:52.490
Ink: I'm no longer angry.

00:56:52.490 --> 00:56:54.390
[Cool till the end]

00:56:54.390 --> 00:56:55.320
Phuak: Helping each other, huh?

00:56:55.320 --> 00:56:55.660
[As for him, he's just a regular brother]

00:56:55.660 --> 00:56:56.720
Ink: Yes, awesome.

00:56:58.420 --> 00:57:00.320
Phuak: Cute, cute.

00:57:00.320 --> 00:57:01.050
Daou: Wait, wait.

00:57:01.050 --> 00:57:01.790
Oat: I'll take her place later!

00:57:01.790 --> 00:57:02.450
Jeff: Let's go in together!

00:57:02.450 --> 00:57:04.250
NuNew: No, we'll go in together!

00:57:04.690 --> 00:57:05.790
Billkin: What!

00:57:06.850 --> 00:57:09.720
Phuak: Wait. Wait. Wait.

00:57:09.720 --> 00:57:11.890
Phuak: "Everyone" means...

00:57:11.890 --> 00:57:13.520
Phuak: I'm included too?

00:57:14.190 --> 00:57:17.620
Billkin: The best sportsmanship award is
that you'll each get an ice cream.

00:57:17.620 --> 00:57:19.770
PD: 1, 2, 3, go!

00:57:29.300 --> 00:57:32.520
[Reward for the best big brother]

00:57:33.290 --> 00:57:36.580
Tay: Don't play with my heart, OK?

00:57:45.990 --> 00:57:49.860
Billkin: OK. So the winner of this mission

00:57:50.150 --> 00:57:51.130
Billkin: is...

00:57:55.020 --> 00:57:57.530
Billkin: Tay and Oat! It's a tie.

00:57:59.560 --> 00:58:00.390
Oat: Brother!

00:58:01.220 --> 00:58:03.280
Tay: We shook hands in the first game.

00:58:04.200 --> 00:58:07.850
Oat: The first game!
What do you think?

00:58:07.900 --> 00:58:09.820
Oat: A meteoric rise!
[A meteoric rise]

00:58:09.820 --> 00:58:13.310
Oat: We did it!
The ugly ducklings have become swans!

00:58:13.370 --> 00:58:16.330
Billkin: Congratulations to Oat and Tay.

00:58:16.410 --> 00:58:19.020
Billkin: I have a gift for you. A gift.

00:58:23.660 --> 00:58:27.540
Billkin:: Cremo Choco Crush Lava ice cream.

00:58:27.930 --> 00:58:29.330
Billkin: Do you know why?

00:58:29.530 --> 00:58:34.170
Billkin: Layers of rich, dense chocolate;
there's molten lava in every bite.

00:58:34.210 --> 00:58:37.130
Billkin: I hope you'll be energized
by the encouragement from Cremo

00:58:37.130 --> 00:58:39.760
Billkin: and carry on
with your next mission.

00:58:39.760 --> 00:58:42.340
Billkin: Good luck.
This is the encouragement from Cremo.

00:58:42.340 --> 00:58:43.950
Everyone: Thank you.

00:58:44.860 --> 00:58:47.060
[Ranking:
Tay & Oat: 3 questions correct = 7 points each]

00:58:47.060 --> 00:58:49.600
[Daou, Ink, NuNew, Jeff & Phuak:
1 question correct = 5 points each]

00:58:59.810 --> 00:59:01.170
Everyone: Slide, slide, slide!

00:59:01.170 --> 00:59:03.100
Everyone: Be careful. Be careful.

00:59:03.690 --> 00:59:04.940
Daou: Where are you going?

00:59:04.940 --> 00:59:06.050
Ink: I... I reached...

00:59:06.050 --> 00:59:08.460
-Ink: I reached first!
-Tay: I reached first!

00:59:08.460 --> 00:59:10.050
Daou: No... Wow...

00:59:19.530 --> 00:59:22.970
PD: Welcome to this test.

00:59:23.010 --> 00:59:28.360
PD: This round
will test your stamina and endurance.

00:59:29.750 --> 00:59:29.820
Endurance fitness test:
the "A, E, I, O, U" Stairs of Hell Battle.

00:59:29.820 --> 00:59:35.860
["A, E, I, O, U" Stairs of Hell Battle]

00:59:36.510 --> 00:59:40.500
All 7 members will draw lots and form pairs
who will go up against each other.

00:59:40.500 --> 00:59:42.090
In the qualifiers,

00:59:42.090 --> 00:59:47.430
a lucky one will automatically advance
to the next round.

00:59:47.430 --> 00:59:49.740
The winners of the qualifiers

00:59:49.760 --> 00:59:53.920
will continue on
to the semi-finals and finals,

00:59:54.000 --> 00:59:56.370
until the final winner is decided.

00:59:56.570 --> 00:59:57.990
The rules are as follows:

00:59:58.240 --> 01:00:00.220
as a referee shouts

01:00:00.340 --> 01:00:01.840
"A, E, I, O, U,"

01:00:02.220 --> 01:00:04.190
both players will race to the top.

01:00:04.470 --> 01:00:06.920
But when the referee says stop

01:00:06.920 --> 01:00:07.240
[Stop!]

01:00:07.240 --> 01:00:08.690
and turns around,

01:00:08.970 --> 01:00:11.390
both players must stop moving immediately.

01:00:11.390 --> 01:00:12.840
If their body moves,

01:00:13.020 --> 01:00:14.190
they must return to the starting line
and start over.

01:00:14.190 --> 01:00:15.490
[Stop!]

01:00:16.190 --> 01:00:19.520
The one who reaches the top
and tears off their name tag first

01:00:19.690 --> 01:00:20.790
will be the winner

01:00:20.870 --> 01:00:22.840
who enters the next round.

01:00:24.570 --> 01:00:24.930
1, 2, 3, go!

01:00:24.930 --> 01:00:27.200
[The draw of the qualifiers begins]

01:00:27.640 --> 01:00:30.970
[If you get the same number,
you'll be opponents]

01:00:31.100 --> 01:00:31.670
Phuak: What are you doing?

01:00:31.670 --> 01:00:33.840
1, 2, 3!
[Will they advance automatically
or play the game?]

01:00:33.840 --> 01:00:34.730
Phuak: Who is it?

01:00:34.730 --> 01:00:35.200
Phuak: 1.

01:00:35.200 --> 01:00:35.640
[Ink vs. Phuak]

01:00:35.640 --> 01:00:36.640
Ink: Me against Phuak?

01:00:36.640 --> 01:00:37.570
Phuak: You got 1?

01:00:38.530 --> 01:00:39.100
Oat: 2.

01:00:39.100 --> 01:00:41.640
Jeff: 2!
[Oat vs. Jeff]

01:00:41.640 --> 01:00:42.600
Tay: And then?

01:00:44.100 --> 01:00:44.690
[NuNew vs. Daou]

01:00:44.690 --> 01:00:47.440
NuNew: How can I win?

01:00:49.240 --> 01:00:51.240
[You're the lucky one]

01:00:51.240 --> 01:00:52.700
Ink: Are you the lucky one?

01:00:53.900 --> 01:00:56.440
It's Tay?
[Tay automatically advances]

01:00:56.680 --> 01:00:57.530
Tay!

01:00:57.530 --> 01:00:58.830
NuNew: Why are you so lucky?

01:00:58.830 --> 01:01:00.970
Tay: I've never been lucky
since I was born.

01:01:00.970 --> 01:01:03.230
Tay: Thank you, "Running Man Thailand"!

01:01:03.870 --> 01:01:04.400
[Everyone is super jealous]

01:01:04.400 --> 01:01:05.730
Ink: What is happening?

01:01:05.970 --> 01:01:07.770
NuNew: Fate has smiled upon you.

01:01:08.090 --> 01:01:09.270
[Finals]

01:01:09.270 --> 01:01:12.440
[The lucky one]

01:01:12.820 --> 01:01:14.370
[Round 1]

01:01:14.790 --> 01:01:16.170
Get ready.
[Ink vs. Phuak]

01:01:17.490 --> 01:01:19.320
[Tay automatically advances]

01:01:19.530 --> 01:01:21.270
Ink: But I learned ballet.

01:01:22.530 --> 01:01:22.890
NuNew: Is that of any help?

01:01:22.890 --> 01:01:23.950
[Will it help?]

01:01:24.330 --> 01:01:24.740
Oat: If you sit on top and slide down first,
it'll be funny, Ink.

01:01:24.740 --> 01:01:27.270
[Will we see Ink show off her dance moves?]

01:01:28.740 --> 01:01:29.760
Tay: A.

01:01:29.760 --> 01:01:31.100
Tay: E.

01:01:31.350 --> 01:01:32.480
Tay: I.

01:01:33.870 --> 01:01:34.530
Tay: A.

01:01:35.020 --> 01:01:35.850
Tay: E.

01:01:36.500 --> 01:01:37.630
Tay: I.

01:01:37.870 --> 01:01:39.240
Tay: O, U.

01:01:39.770 --> 01:01:40.530
Tay: Stop!

01:01:40.570 --> 01:01:41.370
Tay: A.

01:01:41.420 --> 01:01:41.970
[Speeds up through a body slide]

01:01:41.970 --> 01:01:45.670
Tay: E. I. O. U.

01:01:46.640 --> 01:01:47.470
Tay: Stop!

01:01:48.100 --> 01:01:48.900
Tay: A.

01:01:49.070 --> 01:01:49.270
Tay: E. I. O. U.

01:01:49.270 --> 01:01:53.490
[Keeps her balance
and moves forward carefully]

01:01:53.700 --> 01:01:54.500
Tay: Stop!

01:01:58.440 --> 01:01:59.140
[Ink]
[Phuak]

01:01:59.140 --> 01:02:00.540
[A wide gap from the get-go]

01:02:00.830 --> 01:02:02.160
Jeff: Phuak is so smart.

01:02:06.900 --> 01:02:07.700
Tay: A.

01:02:09.090 --> 01:02:09.940
Tay: A.

01:02:10.240 --> 01:02:11.030
Tay: Stop!

01:02:11.900 --> 01:02:12.670
Tay: A.

01:02:12.670 --> 01:02:13.270
[Fierce start, but the result is a mess]

01:02:13.270 --> 01:02:14.230
Tay: Stop!

01:02:24.300 --> 01:02:25.100
Tay: A.

01:02:25.100 --> 01:02:25.900
Tay: E. I.

01:02:25.900 --> 01:02:27.800
Tay: O, U, stop!

01:02:33.640 --> 01:02:34.270
Tay: A.

01:02:35.270 --> 01:02:35.900
Tay: E.

01:02:36.240 --> 01:02:38.640
Tay: I, O, U, stop!

01:02:42.570 --> 01:02:43.500
NuNew: Sliding!

01:02:46.270 --> 01:02:47.900
Sliding!
[His plan is to confuse Ink]

01:02:47.900 --> 01:02:49.440
Tay: A, E, I, O...

01:02:49.440 --> 01:02:50.170
Tay: U, stop!

01:02:52.030 --> 01:02:53.700
Tay: A, E, I, O...

01:02:53.700 --> 01:02:54.580
Tay: U, stop!

01:03:03.490 --> 01:03:07.990
[The two return to
the starting line together]

01:03:08.470 --> 01:03:09.070
Tay: Ready.

01:03:09.070 --> 01:03:11.400
Ink: Wow, no mercy for your little sister!

01:03:12.370 --> 01:03:15.140
Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!

01:03:19.660 --> 01:03:21.610
[Ink is out!]

01:03:22.900 --> 01:03:24.040
Tay: OK.
[Goes easy on her this time]

01:03:24.240 --> 01:03:25.270
Phuak: What?

01:03:26.990 --> 01:03:28.250
Tay: Ready. Continue.

01:03:29.100 --> 01:03:31.580
Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!

01:03:39.140 --> 01:03:40.000
Tay: Continue.

01:03:40.810 --> 01:03:43.470
Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!

01:03:43.470 --> 01:03:44.190
[Ah!]

01:03:44.810 --> 01:03:45.970
Tay: O, U, stop!

01:03:47.140 --> 01:03:48.390
[Ink is out!]

01:03:50.490 --> 01:03:51.250
Ink: It's so hard.

01:03:51.250 --> 01:03:52.800
[Ink starts over again]

01:03:54.240 --> 01:03:55.130
[Phuak's chance has come]

01:03:58.270 --> 01:04:00.940
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:04:00.940 --> 01:04:02.890
[Phuak charges up!]

01:04:05.070 --> 01:04:06.030
Tay: Stop!

01:04:13.240 --> 01:04:14.530
Ink: What's wrong with Phuak?

01:04:14.530 --> 01:04:15.590
NuNew: Why is your face so dirty, Phuak?

01:04:15.590 --> 01:04:17.370
[So miserable]

01:04:21.300 --> 01:04:23.390
Tay: Get ready.
[The tables have turned]

01:04:24.120 --> 01:04:25.840
[It can't end like this]

01:04:27.020 --> 01:04:28.940
[This distance... There's still a chance]

01:04:30.670 --> 01:04:35.870
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:04:35.870 --> 01:04:37.470
[Hoping to reverse the situation
through a body slide]

01:04:39.170 --> 01:04:42.170
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:04:42.170 --> 01:04:43.020
Tay: Stop!

01:04:45.890 --> 01:04:47.400
[Greed leads to loss]

01:04:51.640 --> 01:04:53.790
[Phuak is knocked down]

01:04:54.030 --> 01:04:55.570
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:04:55.570 --> 01:04:57.470
[Ink speeds up]

01:04:57.470 --> 01:04:58.470
Tay: Stop!

01:04:58.980 --> 01:05:00.450
Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!

01:05:01.670 --> 01:05:02.870
Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!

01:05:02.870 --> 01:05:04.790
Phuak: Ink!
[Clenches his teeth and keeps going]

01:05:05.070 --> 01:05:07.030
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:05:07.030 --> 01:05:07.870
Tay: Stop!

01:05:08.110 --> 01:05:09.290
[Phuak follows closely behind]

01:05:10.740 --> 01:05:11.900
NuNew: Not bad.

01:05:11.900 --> 01:05:13.730
-Tay: A, E, I, O, U, stop!
-Ink: Don't!

01:05:13.730 --> 01:05:15.650
[Grabs her ankle in a blink of an eye]

01:05:16.140 --> 01:05:17.520
[I must catch up]

01:05:17.940 --> 01:05:19.170
Ink: Phuak, let go!

01:05:19.900 --> 01:05:21.070
Ink: Phuak!

01:05:21.640 --> 01:05:22.700
Ink: Phuak, let go!

01:05:23.530 --> 01:05:24.470
Ink: Phuak!

01:05:24.470 --> 01:05:25.100
Tay: A.

01:05:25.100 --> 01:05:26.630
Phuak: Ink, Ink, Ink!

01:05:27.240 --> 01:05:29.100
Tay: E, I, O, U, stop!

01:05:29.530 --> 01:05:30.230
Tay: A.

01:05:30.240 --> 01:05:31.740
Phuak: Ink, Ink, Ink!

01:05:32.370 --> 01:05:33.970
Tay: E, I, O, U, stop!

01:05:34.440 --> 01:05:35.140
Phuak: Ink, Ink, Ink!

01:05:35.140 --> 01:05:35.770
Tay: A.

01:05:36.140 --> 01:05:38.140
Tay: E, I, O, U, stop!

01:05:38.310 --> 01:05:39.310
NuNew: She did it.

01:05:41.040 --> 01:05:42.970
[A distance too great to bridge]

01:05:43.240 --> 01:05:44.270
Phuak: Tay, Tay. Give me a miracle.

01:05:44.270 --> 01:05:44.970
[OK!]

01:05:44.970 --> 01:05:51.340
Tay: A, E, I, O, U...

01:05:51.340 --> 01:05:55.970
-Ink: I can't tear it off!
-Tay: U...

01:05:55.970 --> 01:05:57.770
[There's still hope!]

01:05:57.770 --> 01:05:58.470
Ink: Go on! I can't tear it off!

01:05:58.470 --> 01:06:00.790
[Keeps dashing with a shred of hope]

01:06:01.090 --> 01:06:03.000
Ink: Go on! I can't tear it off!

01:06:03.270 --> 01:06:04.700
Oat: He's coming.

01:06:05.470 --> 01:06:10.970
-Ink: I can't tear it off! A bit longer!
-Tay: U...

01:06:10.970 --> 01:06:13.040
Tay: Stop! Stop!

01:06:15.420 --> 01:06:16.940
[It's over...]

01:06:21.100 --> 01:06:23.840
[Ink wins!]

01:06:24.540 --> 01:06:25.740
[Round 2]

01:06:25.940 --> 01:06:26.840
[Jeff vs. Oat]

01:06:26.840 --> 01:06:28.230
Ready, Round 2.

01:06:28.500 --> 01:06:31.100
Phuak: I'll be the referee.
It's the best way to maintain fairness.

01:06:31.100 --> 01:06:33.500
Oat: What? You're a rule breaker!

01:06:33.500 --> 01:06:35.430
Oat: You cheat! Liar!

01:06:35.440 --> 01:06:37.170
Phuak: I'll do my duty fairly.

