01:27:07.910 --> 01:27:10.270
NuNew: Can I hide here
for a while? I'm scared.

01:27:10.270 --> 01:27:12.220
[Who's there?
Kitten goes on alert]

01:27:14.490 --> 01:27:16.870
[At this moment, the stamina boss appears]

01:27:17.870 --> 01:27:19.040
Daou: Hello.

01:27:19.290 --> 01:27:20.190
[Hello there]

01:27:22.390 --> 01:27:23.730
Daou: Hello.

01:27:23.730 --> 01:27:24.820
[Run!]

01:27:25.760 --> 01:27:27.220
Daou: Where are you going?

01:27:27.520 --> 01:27:28.190
[Ah!]

01:27:32.310 --> 01:27:33.150
NuNew: Help!

01:27:35.780 --> 01:27:36.150
Daou: Honestly, I think we should hide.

01:27:36.150 --> 01:27:38.370
[Got to hide now]

01:27:39.990 --> 01:27:42.840
[Planning an ambush]

01:27:44.020 --> 01:27:45.780
Oat: We need to eliminate
one person first.

01:27:45.780 --> 01:27:48.180
Oat: We need to eliminate
one person first.

01:28:07.040 --> 01:28:10.720
[Not Daou, that's a relief]

01:28:12.660 --> 01:28:13.570
Oat: Whoa.

01:28:14.850 --> 01:28:15.320
Jeff: Wait, wait.

01:28:15.320 --> 01:28:16.010
[But you can never
let your guard down in this game]

01:28:16.010 --> 01:28:17.360
Oat: Whoa.

01:28:17.490 --> 01:28:18.160
Jeff: No, this…

01:28:18.160 --> 01:28:19.660
-NuNew: We agreed on this.
-Jeff: My name tag's still on.

01:28:19.660 --> 01:28:20.330
Jeff: We're on the same team.

01:28:20.330 --> 01:28:21.430
Oat: That's what we agreed.

01:28:21.430 --> 01:28:22.170
Jeff: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:28:22.170 --> 01:28:23.930
Tay: I think if this
many of us stick together,

01:28:23.930 --> 01:28:24.870
Tay: he'll run.

01:28:24.950 --> 01:28:26.820
Tay: We need to send one person in
to stir things up.

01:28:26.820 --> 01:28:28.520
Oat: Daou got something really good.

01:28:28.520 --> 01:28:29.800
-Tay: Really? Something good?
-NuNew: What is it?

01:28:29.800 --> 01:28:32.080
Oat: Not sure exactly, but it's top-tier.

01:28:32.080 --> 01:28:32.860
Jeff: First place reward.

01:28:32.860 --> 01:28:33.590
NuNew: Oh, right.
But we don't know what it is.

01:28:33.590 --> 01:28:35.440
[Our target is
Daou with the first-place weapon]

01:28:35.440 --> 01:28:37.700
Jeff: Probably related to the name tags.

01:28:38.690 --> 01:28:39.270
[Cough cough]

01:28:40.970 --> 01:28:41.990
[Startled]

01:28:45.320 --> 01:28:47.050
Daou: So you've teamed up, huh?

01:28:51.820 --> 01:28:52.090
[We're retreating]

01:28:52.090 --> 01:28:53.820
Daou: So you've teamed up, huh?

01:29:02.270 --> 01:29:02.570
Daou: They're planning to set me up.

01:29:02.570 --> 01:29:04.040
[4 against 1; Can't win;
Retreat in order]

01:29:04.040 --> 01:29:05.240
Daou: I'm outta here.

01:29:05.760 --> 01:29:06.560
Daou: Darn it.

01:29:07.400 --> 01:29:08.470
Oat: Over there—he was just there.

01:29:08.470 --> 01:29:09.040
[Group of four]

01:29:09.040 --> 01:29:11.120
Oat: I was with Jeff,
so we didn't come earlier.

01:29:11.120 --> 01:29:13.470
Oat: Let's line up side by side
so everyone feels safe.

01:29:13.470 --> 01:29:14.180
[Hand in hand chasing Daou]

01:29:14.180 --> 01:29:15.920
Oat: Hold hands, walk in a line.

01:29:15.920 --> 01:29:22.080
Oat: Sweep formation, sweep formation.

01:29:22.150 --> 01:29:24.440
Jeff: What if he pretends to be PD?
Think about it.

01:29:24.440 --> 01:29:26.690
Oat: I'm scared he'll
sweep the whole place. Sweep.

01:29:26.690 --> 01:29:28.920
[As expected of Daou; waiting for
a chance to attack from behind]

01:29:30.540 --> 01:29:32.790
[Getting ready to hunt]

01:29:35.970 --> 01:29:36.870
[Sudden brake]

01:29:39.120 --> 01:29:39.540
Oat: He's behind us. He's coming.
What should we do?

01:29:39.540 --> 01:29:41.690
[Daou's over there]

01:29:41.690 --> 01:29:42.430
Oat: Go! Go! Go!

01:29:42.430 --> 01:29:44.180
[Stop right there]

01:29:44.180 --> 01:29:45.100
Oat: Chase!

01:29:50.930 --> 01:29:53.920
Daou: Darn it!

01:29:54.540 --> 01:29:55.800
Daou: That's so nasty.

01:29:56.740 --> 01:29:58.280
[Now's the perfect chance
to take Daou out]

01:29:58.280 --> 01:29:59.280
Oat: Tear his tag!

01:30:01.990 --> 01:30:05.770
[Daou successfully escapes
the 4-person chase]

01:30:06.720 --> 01:30:07.380
Daou: Oh!

01:30:07.790 --> 01:30:09.590
Daou: That's how you wanna play?

01:30:11.590 --> 01:30:14.840
[Even as the stamina boss
ripping tags isn't easy for him]

01:30:15.130 --> 01:30:16.260
Oat: Daou runs fast.

01:30:16.530 --> 01:30:18.790
Oat: See? We need to eliminate him first.

01:30:19.620 --> 01:30:20.760
Tay: Oh, my skill's on cooldown.

01:30:20.760 --> 01:30:21.940
Tay: But the main point right now
is that it’s blocked upstairs.

01:30:21.940 --> 01:30:23.230
Or can we still get out
through another passage?

01:30:23.230 --> 01:30:26.250
Jeff: Then we split into pairs—
one person distracts, the other helps.

01:30:26.250 --> 01:30:27.510
Tay: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:30:27.530 --> 01:30:28.300
Jeff: Let's split up.
Tay and I are a team.

01:30:28.300 --> 01:30:31.640
[Two-person teams chasing Daou]

01:30:31.640 --> 01:30:33.720
[Hiding behind the curtain,
ready to strike]

01:30:33.720 --> 01:30:35.700
Daou: Not planning to rip
anyone else's tag?

01:30:35.700 --> 01:30:37.300
Daou: Just gonna focus on me?

01:30:37.410 --> 01:30:38.630
Daou: Just me, huh?

01:30:39.470 --> 01:30:41.200
Daou: I'm getting serious now.

01:30:45.470 --> 01:30:48.440
[Full sweep for Daou]

01:30:57.540 --> 01:30:59.770
[Ink was hiding well, now has to run]

01:31:03.370 --> 01:31:05.090
[He can't find Daou.
But at least he found Ink]

01:31:05.090 --> 01:31:05.130
Tay: You can't escape, sis.
You can't escape.

01:31:05.130 --> 01:31:06.890
[Jeff and Tay chase after her]

01:31:08.010 --> 01:31:08.700
Ink: Stop!

01:31:09.770 --> 01:31:11.570
[Lie down now]

01:31:12.090 --> 01:31:14.350
Tay: When you eat fish, you flip it first.

01:31:16.670 --> 01:31:18.220
[Ink pulls something out of the pocket]

01:31:21.750 --> 01:31:24.260
Ink: "Grant me the doll's power. Save me!"

01:31:24.710 --> 01:31:27.220
Ink: "Grant me the doll's power. Save me!"

01:31:30.710 --> 01:31:32.110
Jeff: What are you doing?

01:31:36.570 --> 01:31:37.800
Ink: Save me!

01:31:39.510 --> 01:31:40.910
Ink: Save me!

01:31:42.860 --> 01:31:46.080
Ink: Raise the doll
with both hands and shout:

01:31:46.110 --> 01:31:48.730
Ink: "Grant me the doll's power. Save me!"

01:31:48.890 --> 01:31:50.930
Ink: Can instantly summon a guardian

01:31:50.930 --> 01:31:53.550
Ink: to protect you for a set time.

01:31:59.300 --> 01:32:02.230
[Ink's Lucky Doll lasts 10 minutes.
Guardian can protect but can't rip tags]

01:32:02.230 --> 01:32:03.830
Tay: Have you lost your mind?

01:32:04.640 --> 01:32:07.000
[Nothing they can do to Ink now]

01:32:11.040 --> 01:32:13.700
Ink: Then Jeff and Tay,
you two fight each other.

01:32:16.250 --> 01:32:16.480
Ink: No ripping! No ripping!

01:32:16.480 --> 01:32:17.910
[Jeff reveals his weapon]

01:32:18.990 --> 01:32:22.170
[Jeff's weapon is… a water gun]

01:32:22.540 --> 01:32:24.670
Jeff: I choose "Rapid Stream Finisher."

01:32:24.670 --> 01:32:25.930
Jeff: It's a water gun.

01:32:33.090 --> 01:32:35.570
[Trying hard to spray Ink's name tag]

01:32:37.040 --> 01:32:40.270
[Great aim]

01:32:40.790 --> 01:32:43.590
[But with the guardian, it might not hit]

01:32:45.120 --> 01:32:47.020
[Ink's powerful guardians]

01:32:47.460 --> 01:32:49.390
Ink: Why aren't you attacking Tay?

01:32:51.320 --> 01:32:52.920
Tay: See you in 10 minutes, sis.

01:32:52.920 --> 01:32:54.270
Jeff: Ten minutes?

01:32:54.370 --> 01:32:54.680
[Ten minutes with
the guardians by her side]

01:32:54.680 --> 01:32:55.690
Jeff: Oh man.

01:32:57.540 --> 01:32:59.750
[Three bullets total, one already used]

01:33:02.750 --> 01:33:04.680
Ink: That was so scary just now.

01:33:05.250 --> 01:33:07.800
Ink: Let's go, bro, follow me.

01:33:08.110 --> 01:33:09.180
Ink: Where should we go?

01:33:09.180 --> 01:33:13.020
Ink: Now we can walk without worrying.
[Staying alive thanks to the guardians]

01:33:14.320 --> 01:33:16.400
[Keep searching for other members]

01:33:16.400 --> 01:33:17.130
Tay: Not this room.

01:33:17.130 --> 01:33:18.560
Tay: Only this locked room is left.

01:33:18.560 --> 01:33:20.160
[Could someone still be hiding here?]

01:33:20.190 --> 01:33:20.510
[Wasted trip]

01:33:20.510 --> 01:33:21.310
Tay: Nothing.

01:33:24.210 --> 01:33:25.580
Tay: Maybe there's something over there?

01:33:25.580 --> 01:33:26.410
Jeff: Maybe.

01:33:29.860 --> 01:33:31.650
[Daou is lying in ambush over there!]

01:33:32.520 --> 01:33:33.830
[A tough opponent]

01:33:33.830 --> 01:33:37.320
Daou: Come on, you two.
Help each other out.

01:33:37.440 --> 01:33:38.160
Daou: Help each other out.

01:33:38.160 --> 01:33:40.270
[Daou proposes an alliance]

01:33:40.440 --> 01:33:41.930
Daou: I know what you have.

01:33:41.960 --> 01:33:43.220
Jeff: I have a water gun.

01:33:43.220 --> 01:33:44.600
-Daou: Spray water and he's out.
-Jeff: Yes.

01:33:44.600 --> 01:33:45.860
Jeff: How did you know?

01:33:46.020 --> 01:33:47.750
Daou: I guessed from the score.

01:33:48.730 --> 01:33:50.500
Jeff: Wanna team up with me, Daou?

01:33:50.500 --> 01:33:52.280
Jeff: I'm literally exposing
my back to you.

01:33:52.280 --> 01:33:53.740
-Daou: Sure.
-Jeff: Daou.

01:33:53.890 --> 01:33:56.480
Jeff: Let's cooperate.
It'll be easier to move.

01:33:56.480 --> 01:33:57.270
Daou: Who do you think we should find?
Oat is the toughest one.

01:33:57.270 --> 01:33:58.310
[Let's team up and take Oat out first!]

01:33:58.310 --> 01:34:01.220
Tay: Wait… Daou…
Has anyone been eliminated yet?

01:34:03.520 --> 01:34:03.550
[Right then, the prey appears]

01:34:03.550 --> 01:34:06.280
Tay: Wait… Daou…
Has anyone been eliminated yet?

01:34:09.480 --> 01:34:12.520
Tay: Use the item!

01:34:12.540 --> 01:34:14.960
Tay: Use the item!

01:34:17.140 --> 01:34:18.720
[Tay is holding something!]

01:34:19.200 --> 01:34:21.520
[What's Tay's weapon?]

01:34:22.340 --> 01:34:23.330
Tay: Oat!

01:34:23.430 --> 01:34:24.340
Tay: Oat!

01:34:26.470 --> 01:34:28.030
Tay: Your fate...

01:34:30.220 --> 01:34:31.160
Tay: Your fate...

01:34:31.160 --> 01:34:33.460
[Not sure what it does
but the target is definitely Oat]

01:34:40.430 --> 01:34:41.610
Tay: Your fate...

01:34:44.310 --> 01:34:45.980
Tay: is in my hands.

01:34:46.620 --> 01:34:47.940
[Oat's fate depends on this die!]

01:34:53.150 --> 01:34:54.350
Phuak: Will it be Oat?

01:34:59.480 --> 01:35:01.840
[Phuak]

01:35:02.340 --> 01:35:03.030
Oat: Yay!

01:35:03.030 --> 01:35:03.630
[Oat survives!]

01:35:03.630 --> 01:35:05.570
-Oat: Not me.
-Phuak: Then who is it?

01:35:05.570 --> 01:35:06.350
Oat: Phuak.

01:35:06.420 --> 01:35:06.570
Phuak: What?

01:35:06.570 --> 01:35:08.230
[As soon as the weapon use ends]

01:35:08.230 --> 01:35:08.890
[The chase begins immediately]

01:35:08.890 --> 01:35:11.460
Phuak: Wait, wait.

01:35:11.790 --> 01:35:12.950
[Daou, who's been observing all along
launches an attack!]

01:35:12.950 --> 01:35:15.470
Phuak: Wait, wait.

01:35:15.470 --> 01:35:17.210
[The duel resumes]

01:35:17.210 --> 01:35:18.440
Phuak: Daou, Daou!

01:35:18.440 --> 01:35:18.600
Phuak: Daou, Daou!

01:35:18.600 --> 01:35:20.970
[Daou locks onto Oat]

01:35:20.970 --> 01:35:22.970
Oat: Om—invisible, Om—invisible.

01:35:23.480 --> 01:35:23.640
Oat: Om—invisible, Om—invisible.

01:35:23.640 --> 01:35:26.450
[Oat's roar]

01:35:28.740 --> 01:35:31.780
Oat: Om Om Om—invisible.

01:35:32.170 --> 01:35:32.890
Oat: Om.

01:35:33.280 --> 01:35:35.290
[Chants a spell
and puts on an invisibility cloak]

01:35:35.440 --> 01:35:36.430
Oat: Om.

01:35:37.070 --> 01:35:37.770
[Limited to one minute.
Oat's weapon: Magic Cloak]

01:35:37.770 --> 01:35:40.430
-Daou: He disappeared.
-Jeff: Where did Oat go?

01:35:41.540 --> 01:35:42.870
Jeff: Where did Oat go?

01:35:43.030 --> 01:35:44.090
Jeff: Where is Oat?

01:35:44.110 --> 01:35:46.600
[With the cloak's power
Oat escapes from Daou]

01:35:46.600 --> 01:35:48.220
Oat: Stop, stop.

01:35:48.650 --> 01:35:49.270
Oat: Stop.

01:35:51.730 --> 01:35:54.890
[Time 00:23:28]

01:35:55.200 --> 01:35:57.010
-Phuak: What is that?
-Daou: Look—nothing there.

01:35:57.010 --> 01:35:57.700
Phuak: What?

01:35:57.700 --> 01:35:58.370
Daou: It's nothing, bro.

01:35:58.370 --> 01:35:59.150
Phuak: Use the item.

01:35:59.150 --> 01:35:59.810
Daou: What?

01:36:00.010 --> 01:36:01.140
Phuak: Use the item.

01:36:02.290 --> 01:36:03.420
Phuak: Use the item.

01:36:05.890 --> 01:36:07.020
Phuak: Use the item.

01:36:09.420 --> 01:36:10.980
[Phuak — Cold Iron Fist
If the rope hits the opponent,]

01:36:11.000 --> 01:36:14.010
[it can freeze them in place.
Usable once, lasts 30 seconds]

01:36:14.530 --> 01:36:16.860
[Here's the chance!]

01:36:17.500 --> 01:36:18.660
-Daou: How many seconds?
-Phuak: Jeff, come here.

01:36:18.660 --> 01:36:18.930
[Jeff quietly approaches Daou]

01:36:18.930 --> 01:36:20.990
Phuak: Thirty seconds. NuNew, come.

01:36:21.890 --> 01:36:24.130
[Water gun ready to fire!]

01:36:24.280 --> 01:36:25.990
Daou: I've just been
standing here quietly.

01:36:25.990 --> 01:36:26.940
Daou: Just stand here?

01:36:26.940 --> 01:36:27.400
[NuNew asks to join the brothers' fight]

01:36:27.400 --> 01:36:28.830
Phuak: Got it, got it!

01:36:28.950 --> 01:36:33.470
Daou: NuNew, rip Phuak's tag! Rip his tag!

01:36:33.720 --> 01:36:35.620
[Immediately flanks from behind!]

01:36:36.020 --> 01:36:37.070
Daou: Rip Phuak's tag! Hurry!

01:36:37.070 --> 01:36:38.290
Daou: Rip Phuak's tag! Hurry!

01:36:38.290 --> 01:36:39.610
-Daou: Jeff, is it done?
-Jeff: Time's up.

01:36:39.610 --> 01:36:41.340
Jeff: I sprayed him with water.

01:36:41.820 --> 01:36:44.150
Daou: Rip Phuak's tag! Hurry!

01:36:44.200 --> 01:36:44.880
Daou: Jeff!

01:36:46.880 --> 01:36:47.880
-Daou: Done yet?
-Jeff: Time's up.

01:36:47.880 --> 01:36:49.480
Jeff: I sprayed him already.

01:36:49.870 --> 01:36:53.750
[The water gun hits
the name tag perfectly!]

01:36:53.940 --> 01:36:56.430
[Daou's name tag was hit head-on]

01:36:59.150 --> 01:37:01.670
Commander R: Daou out.

01:37:01.670 --> 01:37:04.810
Commander R: Daou out.

01:37:06.250 --> 01:37:08.680
-Commander R: Daou out.
-Oat: Oh!

01:37:08.820 --> 01:37:11.680
-Commander R: Daou out.
-Oat: Daou?

01:37:11.780 --> 01:37:13.310
Oat: Yes! Yes!

01:37:13.510 --> 01:37:15.310
Oat: Nothing to be afraid of now.

01:37:15.930 --> 01:37:16.810
Daou is out.

01:37:18.940 --> 01:37:20.080
Oat: It's my time.

01:37:21.130 --> 01:37:22.930
Tay: There are 5 people left now.

01:37:23.550 --> 01:37:26.940
Tay: Ink isn't a threat.
Oat and Jeff are the scary ones.

01:37:27.050 --> 01:37:29.540
Tay: Ink is also waiting for
the "Deathly Love Curse" effect to end.

01:37:29.540 --> 01:37:31.750
[Tay's target is Ink!]

01:37:33.010 --> 01:37:33.940
[Tay is approaching Ink as planned]

01:37:33.940 --> 01:37:35.190
Tay: So there's a time limit, right?

01:37:35.190 --> 01:37:36.290
Ink: Why?

01:37:36.310 --> 01:37:37.390
Tay: I won't do anything to you.

01:37:37.390 --> 01:37:41.590
Tay: Let's go find someone later
and take them out.

01:37:41.640 --> 01:37:43.970
Tay: You can help me
eliminate someone too.

01:37:43.970 --> 01:37:46.070
Ink: Let's form an alliance first.

01:37:46.400 --> 01:37:47.330
Ink: Deal.

01:37:48.280 --> 01:37:49.500
Tay: Let's go.

01:37:49.500 --> 01:37:50.720
Ink: We go to the temple
every New Year's Day.

01:37:50.720 --> 01:37:51.570
Tay: OK.

01:37:51.570 --> 01:37:52.430
Ink: We go to the temple
on January 1 every year.

01:37:52.430 --> 01:37:54.130
-Tay: Then let's go take the others out.
-Ink: OK.

01:37:54.130 --> 01:37:55.490
Tay: Who should it be? You choose.

01:37:55.490 --> 01:37:56.450
[Startled]

01:37:57.000 --> 01:37:58.850
Tay: I'll take them out for you.

01:37:59.590 --> 01:38:00.660
-Ink: I was so touched just now.
-Tay: Who, who?

01:38:00.660 --> 01:38:01.840
[Talking while launching
a surprise attack!]

01:38:01.880 --> 01:38:03.810
Ink: I was really touched just now.

01:38:04.790 --> 01:38:04.840
Tay: Let's go. Who, who?

01:38:04.840 --> 01:38:06.620
[Was he just trying to put an arm
around Ink's shoulders?]

01:38:06.620 --> 01:38:08.400
-Tay: Pick someone.
-Ink: OK, OK.

01:38:08.400 --> 01:38:08.940
[Both pretend nothing happened]

01:38:08.940 --> 01:38:11.050
Tay: We need to trust each other first.

01:38:11.050 --> 01:38:13.750
[But right after, Tay starts attacking!]

01:38:15.490 --> 01:38:18.970
[The moment he spots an opening,
he strikes from behind]

01:38:20.080 --> 01:38:21.300
Ink: Hey, Tay.

01:38:22.690 --> 01:38:24.890
[They lose their balance]

01:38:25.210 --> 01:38:28.430
[They're already trying this hard.
Why is the name tag still so stubborn?]

01:38:28.710 --> 01:38:30.380
Ink: Buddha is watching.

01:38:32.940 --> 01:38:34.860
[Ink refuses to give up!]

01:38:35.360 --> 01:38:37.720
[This good big brother
won't give up either]

01:38:37.720 --> 01:38:40.200
Tay: Sis, we're like family.

01:38:41.740 --> 01:38:44.140
Tay: One, two!

01:38:48.880 --> 01:38:52.150
[Ink's whole body lifts off the ground]

01:38:56.920 --> 01:38:58.870
Ink: I was literally dragged off my feet!

01:38:58.870 --> 01:39:01.800
-Tay: It's stuck too tight.
-Ink: It's really tight!

01:39:03.430 --> 01:39:06.600
Ink: The nice Tay from yesterday
is gone now.

01:39:07.610 --> 01:39:07.750
