NuNew: Go help me rip Oat's name tag.

01:43:46.390 --> 01:43:46.790
Commander R: NuNew out.

01:43:46.790 --> 01:43:48.820
[Before he could even react
NuNew out]

01:43:48.820 --> 01:43:52.100
Commander R: NuNew out.

