Jeff: There aren't
many people left now, bro.

01:45:10.840 --> 01:45:11.650
Oat: Okay.

01:45:11.830 --> 01:45:13.890
Oat: We can settle it here if you want.

01:45:14.580 --> 01:45:16.620
