01:45:28.580 --> 01:45:30.180
Oat: No, no.

01:45:36.020 --> 01:45:37.280
Jeff: Oat.

01:45:37.400 --> 01:45:38.440
Oat: No, no.

01:45:38.550 --> 01:45:39.250
Jeff: Oat.

01:45:39.370 --> 01:45:40.650
Daou: He's so strong at pulling people.

01:45:40.650 --> 01:45:41.390
Jeff: Oat.

01:45:41.390 --> 01:45:44.630
Daou: That pulling force is insane,
so we need to…

01:45:45.780 --> 01:45:48.440
[Tay launches a sudden ambush]

01:45:52.440 --> 01:45:54.840
[But still misses…]

01:45:54.970 --> 01:45:56.720
Daou: Come on, let's surround him!
Everyone together!

01:45:56.720 --> 01:45:59.680
Oat: Om. Om. Om.

01:45:59.830 --> 01:46:01.690
-Oat: Invisible.
-Daou: He used an item.

01:46:01.690 --> 01:46:05.020
[Om, invisible]

01:46:05.020 --> 01:46:07.950
Oat: Om, invisible, om.

01:46:10.320 --> 01:46:12.890
Oat: Om, invisible, om.

01:46:14.860 --> 01:46:14.880
[I'm invisible
Pretend you can't see me]

01:46:14.880 --> 01:46:17.800
Oat: Om, invisible, om.

01:46:18.130 --> 01:46:19.670
Jeff: Huh? Where did Oat go?

01:46:19.700 --> 01:46:22.170
[Run]

01:46:22.170 --> 01:46:24.320
Jeff: Huh? Where did he go? Oat!

01:46:26.710 --> 01:46:27.840
