01:47:25.260 --> 01:47:28.120
Oat: You've gotta use
your brain, my friend.

01:47:28.680 --> 01:47:31.650
Oat: Om, om, invisible.

01:47:32.290 --> 01:47:34.150
-Daou: Hey, Oat.
-Jeff: Hey, Oat.

01:47:35.380 --> 01:47:37.580
Daou: Let's go. I think he went that way.

01:47:37.790 --> 01:47:39.880
Daou: I think...

01:47:39.900 --> 01:47:42.260
Daou: Yeah, he went that way.

01:47:43.940 --> 01:47:44.480
Daou: Where did he run off to?

01:47:44.480 --> 01:47:47.450
[One minute is up!!]

01:47:49.410 --> 01:47:50.460
Jeff: It's over.

01:47:50.540 --> 01:47:51.820
Jeff: The truth is out.

01:47:57.130 --> 01:47:58.080
Daou: Are we taking out Jeff?

01:47:58.080 --> 01:47:58.700
Oat: We can.

01:47:58.700 --> 01:48:00.780
-Daou: No.
-Oat: Let's take Jeff out first.

01:48:00.780 --> 01:48:01.950
Daou: Hold him! Hold him!

01:48:01.950 --> 01:48:04.480
Daou: Jeff—it takes 3 people
