01:48:05.540 --> 01:48:06.680
Tay: Oat.

01:48:07.550 --> 01:48:09.080
Daou: This is really tough.

01:48:11.300 --> 01:48:13.160
[Keep smiling]

01:48:14.400 --> 01:48:16.940
