Daou: Don't want that?

01:49:31.460 --> 01:49:33.070
Daou: Let me show you
what it feels like to be prey.

01:49:33.070 --> 01:49:33.760
Daou: Tay.

01:49:34.880 --> 01:49:36.340
Daou: Don't want that?

01:49:36.340 --> 01:49:39.070
Daou: Let me show you
what it feels like to be prey.

01:49:40.080 --> 01:49:41.130
Daou: Tay.

01:49:45.020 --> 01:49:46.810
Daou: Heh, still not enough.

01:49:53.470 --> 01:49:54.470
Daou: Jeff, Jeff!

01:49:54.860 --> 01:49:57.390
Daou: Jeff Satur—now! Get up!

01:50:00.990 --> 01:50:03.350
[Immediately switches target!]

01:50:04.200 --> 01:50:05.220
Daou: Ah!

01:50:05.800 --> 01:50:06.170
Daou: Satur!

01:50:06.170 --> 01:50:08.900
[Solid as a rock,
he is Jeff Satur]

01:50:08.900 --> 01:50:10.280
Daou: Satur!

01:50:12.940 --> 01:50:14.320
Jeff: Oh my. I'm dying!

01:50:15.880 --> 01:50:17.220
Jeff: Oh my. I'm dying!

01:50:18.780 --> 01:50:20.710
Daou: You want to go head-to-head?

01:50:23.690 --> 01:50:25.200
Tay: Laugh him to death!
Make him laugh till he passes out!

01:50:25.200 --> 01:50:26.940
Tay: Hurry, make him laugh!

01:50:31.980 --> 01:50:33.020
Tay: Alright. Almost got it!

01:50:33.020 --> 01:50:34.360
-Jeff: It works?
-Tay: Almost there!

01:50:34.360 --> 01:50:36.090
Tay: Almost got it—tickle him!

01:50:38.430 --> 01:50:39.700
Tay: Tickle him!

01:50:42.390 --> 01:50:43.630
Daou: Ah, Tay…

01:50:45.050 --> 01:50:47.530
[Successfully rips off Daou's name tag!]

01:50:53.230 --> 01:50:54.550
Tay: Sorry.

01:50:54.600 --> 01:50:55.830
Tay: Sorry.

01:50:55.850 --> 01:50:57.240
Daou: It's actually good
you eliminated me.

01:50:57.240 --> 01:50:57.940
Jeff: Why?

01:50:57.950 --> 01:50:59.150
Daou: I'm exhausted.

01:51:01.530 --> 01:51:02.660
Daou: I'm going home

01:51:06.020 --> 01:51:06.040
[Daou out]

01:51:06.040 --> 01:51:08.620
Commander R: Daou out.

01:51:08.690 --> 01:51:11.390
Commander R: Daou out.

01:51:16.360 --> 01:51:20.320
[In the first round,
who will be the winner?]

01:51:23.010 --> 01:51:28.130
[Step on it, hit the gas,
full speed ahead]

01:51:28.540 --> 01:51:30.670
[The man who never lets his target
slip away]

01:51:30.670 --> 01:51:33.220
Jeff: Allies? There are
no real allies now.

01:51:34.750 --> 01:51:37.240
[Superstar Jeff Satur,
offensive player]

01:51:37.450 --> 01:51:40.030
[The only way to survive
is to fight back!]

01:51:40.410 --> 01:51:41.990
[Hiding behind the door]

01:51:42.030 --> 01:51:43.990
[A master of invisible
impossible to be discovered]

01:51:47.010 --> 01:51:49.500
Tay: First place isn't happening.
