01:52:02.780 --> 01:52:04.310
Tay: He's getting serious.

01:52:04.570 --> 01:52:06.500
Tay: He's really getting serious.

01:52:14.860 --> 01:52:16.290
Tay: Help!

01:52:16.340 --> 01:52:16.990
Tay: Help!

01:52:17.620 --> 01:52:19.640
Tay: Your parents didn't send you
here to risk your life!

01:52:19.640 --> 01:52:20.720
Tay: To live like this?

01:52:20.720 --> 01:52:24.050
Jeff: Isn't this Running Man?
