01:52:24.550 --> 01:52:25.810
Tay: Don't hit the dog!

01:52:26.680 --> 01:52:27.940
Tay: Don't hit the dog!

01:52:31.430 --> 01:52:32.400
Tay: Come on.

01:52:32.600 --> 01:52:33.640
Tay: Together.

01:52:33.690 --> 01:52:34.890
Tay: At the same time.

