Jeff: Tay actually bites people.

01:52:42.160 --> 01:52:43.120
Jeff: Tay!

01:52:55.370 --> 01:52:57.010
Tay: Hey—I almost got it! Almost got it!

01:52:57.010 --> 01:53:00.070
[Tay gets to Jeff's name tag first]

01:53:02.660 --> 01:53:08.560
[Who will survive, who will be out?!]

01:53:13.370 --> 01:53:15.590
[Rip]

01:53:17.150 --> 01:53:20.140
The competition has officially ended.

01:53:20.260 --> 01:53:23.190
So now, between Tay and Jeff,

01:53:23.200 --> 01:53:27.030
who do you think is most likely
to be Running Man's strongest agent?

01:53:27.250 --> 01:53:27.920
Phuak: Jeff.

01:53:27.920 --> 01:53:29.380
-Ink: Jeff.
NuNew: I choose Jeff.

01:53:29.380 --> 01:53:30.830
Phuak: Tay is too soft-hearted.

01:53:30.830 --> 01:53:33.380
NuNew: But Jeff...
But Tay is strong.

01:53:33.510 --> 01:53:35.190
Ink: Tay is super strong.

01:53:35.230 --> 01:53:38.090
Daou: Since no one's
on Tay's side, I'll choose Tay.

01:53:39.050 --> 01:53:41.450
NuNew: I want to know
who it is. I'm curious.

01:53:54.970 --> 01:53:55.950
Oat: Here we go.

01:54:01.600 --> 01:54:03.450
PD: I'll count to one, two, three.

01:54:03.450 --> 01:54:04.800
PD: Then both of you turn around

01:54:04.800 --> 01:54:05.700
PD: to reveal who the winner is.

01:54:05.700 --> 01:54:08.400
[As you expected]

01:54:08.400 --> 01:54:08.830
One.

01:54:09.630 --> 01:54:10.600
Two.

01:54:10.600 --> 01:54:12.970
[Is Jeff the first winner?]

01:54:13.080 --> 01:54:14.320
[Or...]

01:54:14.320 --> 01:54:15.170
Two.

01:54:16.660 --> 01:54:19.720
[Tay can turn the tide.]

01:54:19.990 --> 01:54:22.830
One, two, three.

01:54:36.680 --> 01:54:37.680
Tay: Almost got it!

01:54:37.680 --> 01:54:41.740
[RUNININING MAN]
[The first battle]

01:54:41.780 --> 01:54:45.000
[Who will be the winner
between Jeff and Tay?]

01:54:56.750 --> 01:55:01.490
